      <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color:#052540;">We will update you once on account verification.</p>

      <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color:#052540;">
        Thank you.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color:#052540;">
        Sincerely,<br>MortgageBrokers.com.
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= render :partial => "layouts/mailers/email_footer"%>

  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
